\F[sora_smile]Sora: "At the previous park, the hint was in an obvious
place, so..."
\F[sora_laugh]Sora: "Ah, I knew it! I found it right away!"
\F[sora_trouble]Sora: "This is... someone's three sizes, isn't it?"
\F[sora_trouble]Sora: "I-I don't know this... Is there no other hint?"

\F[sora_trouble]Sora: "Anyway... it must be a girl with big breasts. Who
could it be? Torii-san? Seiryu-san? Hmm, I can't figure it
out. I know it's not Himawari-chan..."

\F[sora_smile]Sora: "There's something written on the edge... 2-B! Good
thing I didn't miss it. Let's go check it out quickly!"

\F[sora_smile]Sora: "This way leads to the staff room... so it would be
quicker to go to 2-B from the opposite direction, right?"

\F[sora_smile]Sora: "This way leads to the staff room... so it would be
quicker to go to 2-B from the opposite direction, right?"

mean those numbers that look like three sizes are Akane-
chan's?..."

\F[sora_smile]Sora: "Wow~. I guess boys really do prefer girls with bigger
breasts, huh?"

\F[sora_laugh]Sora: "But... now that I've got three gold coins, I can go
to the live concert with Himawari-chan again♪"

"Let's learn the blindfold study method!" For more details,
